Paper: hep-th/0301227

Date: 2003-01-28

Title: Constant magnetic field and 2d non-commutative inverted oscillator

Authors: Stefano Bellucci

Comments: 7 pages, LaTeX file, no figures, PACS number

We consider a two-dimensional non-commutative inverted oscillator in thepresence of a constant magnetic field, coupled to the system in a``symplectic'' and ``Poisson'' way. We show that it has a discrete energyspectrum for some value of the magnetic field.